'''爱湾'''（{{lang-la|Sinus Amoris}}）是[[月球|月球]][[静海|静海]]东北的一处小[[月海|月海]]区。大小为200-300公里，中心[[月面坐标|月面坐标]]为{{Coord|18.1|N|39.1|E|globe:Moon}}<ref name=gazetteer>{{cite web
 |url         = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5559
 |title       = Sinus Amoris
 |work        = Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature
 |publisher   = International Astronomical Union (IAU) Working Group for Planetary System Nomenclature (WGPSN)
 |date        = 2010-10-18
 |accessdate  = 2015-06-11
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/68sQ5h96c?url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5559
 |archivedate = 2012-07-03
 |deadurl     = no
}}</ref>。其名称首次出现在1974年出版的美国军事测绘局为美国宇航局绘制的月图上<ref name=LTO_1974>{{cite book
 |work         = Sheet LTO-43D2: Franck
 |title        = NASA Lunar Topographic Orthophotomap (based on Apollo 15 and 17 photos). Scale 1:250,000
 |edition      = ed. 1
